152
00:10:46,060 --> 00:10:51,050
It seems that you only have these two choices.

153
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:56,230
The Cave Master of Qianyue Sect is the most respected.

154
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:58,520
Among his nine leaders,

155
00:10:58,520 --> 00:11:01,270
