156
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:04,420
Plotting a rebellion is not a serious offence.

157
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:08,040
Losing (a serious "crime") leads to a death penalty.

158
00:11:10,370 --> 00:11:14,950
Back then, you also had murdered your leader.

159
00:11:15,950 --> 00:11:19,630
Being a leader is much more comfortable

160
00:11:19,630 --> 00:11:22,290
