161
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:26,590
Shangguan Qiu Yue’s capabilities are fathomless.

162
00:11:26,590 --> 00:11:29,310
Are you worried about this?

163
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:35,270
I have a plan to help you…

164
00:11:38,510 --> 00:11:41,470
